<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>心之所乡，一苇以航——校友代表周飞侠的毕业赠言</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; text-wrap: wrap; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">尊敬的各位领导、敬爱的老师们，亲爱的学弟学妹们：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; text-indent: 37px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">大家好！我是2007届校友周飞侠，满怀激动与感慨，非常荣幸今天能够站在母校毕业典礼这个意义非凡的讲台上，与大家分享我的一些感悟和体会。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240625/1719308988280000211.jpg" title="1719308988280000211.jpg" alt="1719308988280000211.jpg" width="600" height="" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.15789em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">当我凝视着你们那一张张充满朝气与憧憬的年轻面庞时，往昔的记忆如潮水般涌上心头，让我仿佛穿越时光回到了曾经的自己。那是2005年，我怀着对知识的渴求和对未来的期待，踏入了江西软件职业技术大学，选择了软件设计专业。在母校的这片沃土里，我认真学习软件技术知识，不断提升专业能力；我始终相信学好软件，可以改变命运，能够报效祖国。在这里，我努力践行“人品好、英语好、计算机好”的“三好一专、十一工程”育人体系，牢记“创业创新、知识管理”校训，在毕业后的职业生涯中，软件专业培养并塑造了我的职业进程，校训精神深深地影响了我的创业，让我有勇气去面对一切挑战，所以，大学生涯是我人生中极其重要且难忘的一段旅程。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.15789em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">在毕业后的日子里，我凭借着母校赋予我的扎实专业能力和不断进取的精神，先后在浙江用友、小米集团、北京字节跳动等诸多优秀且极具影响力的公司工作，有幸积累了丰富多样的经验与知识。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.15789em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">而在2019年，经过深思熟虑后，我毅然决然地踏上了创业的征程，开启了经营浙江卓星未来科技集团的道路。浙江卓星未来科技集团，是一家集零售、供应链、技术研发和专业服务为一体的综合性数字科技集团，聚焦人工智能、大数据、物联网、数字化等前沿科技，致力于为客户提供领先的综合性解决方案，给消费者带来更好的服务体验。形成了从卓星颜选、卓星数智、卓星未来、卓星产服、卓星金融五大核心品牌全产业链业务。一路走来，其中的艰辛不言而喻，汗水与泪水交织，但我从未有过一丝一毫的后悔。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240625/1719309026831013693.jpg" title="1719309026831013693.jpg" alt="1719309026831013693.jpg" width="600" height="" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">亲爱的学弟学妹们，我想要诚挚地对你们说，未来是一片广</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">袤</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">无</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">垠</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">且充满了无限可能的天地。当你们即将离开这熟悉的校园，踏入社会时，你们必然会面临各种各样的挑战与考验，但请不要心生畏惧。就如同曾经的我一样，勇敢地张开翅膀，向着自己心中的梦想奋力翱翔。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">在今后的工作和生活中，一定要保持一颗持续学习的赤诚之心。因为我们所处的这个时代变化速度超乎想象，只有不断学习新的知识和技能，才能够紧跟时代的步伐，不被淘汰。千万不要将自己局限于大学所学的专业领域，秉承“创业创新、知识管理”的校训，要勇敢地去尝试不同的方向，努力拓展自己的视野和认知边界，去挖掘自身更多的潜力。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">要深刻地认识到学会与人合作的重要性。一个人的力量毕竟是有限的，但团队的力量却可以是无穷无尽的。在与他人合作的过程中，要学会耐心倾听他人的意见和建议，尊重每一个人的独特之处，充分发挥每个人的优势，通过齐心协力共同去创造出更大的价值。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">同时，必须要有坚定如磐石的信念和百折不挠的精神。当遇到困难与挫折时，不要轻易地选择放弃，要始终相信自己一定拥有克服一切艰难险阻的能力。就像我在创业的艰难过程中，也遭遇了数不清的艰难险阻，但我始终坚守着自己内心的那份执着，坚信自己当初的选择，凭借着顽强的毅力咬牙坚持了下来。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">最后，我要衷心地感谢我的母校，感谢每一位曾经辛勤教导过我的老师，是你们用渊博的知识和无尽的关怀，给予了我不断前行的动力和勇气，让我有了今天这样小小的成就。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">亲爱的学弟学妹们，愿你们带着母校的殷切期望和深深祝福，满怀信心与勇气，勇敢地踏上属于你们的全新征程，去肆意书写属于你们的辉煌人生。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;">谢谢大家！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.1875em; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; cursor: text; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%;"><br/></span></p><p><strong>校友简介<br/></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">周飞侠，男，汉族，中共党员，籍贯江西南昌。江西软件职业技术大学2005级软件设计专业，2015年取得浙江大学本科学历，毕业后先后在浙江用友、小米集团、北京字节跳动等公司工作，2019年至今经营浙江卓星未来科技集团有限公司，从事影视娱乐经纪、广告创意营销、互联网品牌电商三大业务板块及产业资源整合业务，现任浙江卓星未来科技集团有限公司董事长、网星梦工厂浙江公司总经理、小米金融事业部高级顾问、颜选生活品牌创始人。</span></p>